data.description: Welcome to the Fulton floor plan at 9945 Winged Elm Street!  A stunning 6-bedroom, 4.5-bath home located in the highly coveted neighborhood of Coosaw Preserve.  Meticulously maintained and showcasing impeccable craftsmanship, this home exudes elegance and comfort throughout.  Step inside to discover an open concept floor plan that seamlessly connects the main living areas, perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. The first floor features durable laminate flooring, adding a touch of sophistication and best of all, easy maintenance.  The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with modern Frigidaire appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinet and counter space. Escape to the screened-in porch and unwind while overlooking the large backyard with a serene pond view.This outdoor oasis provides the ideal setting for relaxation, entertaining, and enjoying the beautiful South Carolina weather.  With six generously sized bedrooms, including a luxurious primary suite, this home offers plenty of space for the whole family as well as guests.  Not only does this home offer exceptional convenience to I26, Boeing, Bosch, Cummins, Mercedes, as well as restaurants, grocery stores, and shopping...  But it also resides within a desirable school district, ensuring access to excellent educational opportunities.  Coosaw Preserve also enhances the living experience with resident amenities.  Homeowners can spend leisurely afternoons by the community pool or watch their children create lasting memories on the playground.  Don't miss out on this extraordinary opportunity to schedule a showing today, and discover the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and community that awaits you.
